      <p class="text-sm text-text-light leading-relaxed italic">Dolphin Centrifuge explains the difference between purifier and clarifier disc stack centrifuges operating at 8,000+ Gs. A purifier separates three phases (two liquids plus solids) using a gravity disc; a clarifier removes solids from a single liquid phase. Dolphin Centrifuge converts disc centrifuges between configurations for all models.</p>
